</p>
<p align="left">
    3.10.4. notification to applicable cattle associations;
</p>
<p align="left">
    3.10.5. forfeiture of any prizes or prize money already received or to be received; and/or
</p>
<p align="left">
    3.10.6. the levy of a charge for the recovery of the reasonable costs incurred by the Rules Committee, the Appeals Committee, the Manager and/or the
    Organiser in relation to the violation(s).
</p>
<p align="left">
    3.11. Penalties for violation are at the absolute discretion of the Organiser.
</p>
<p align="left">
    3.12. The decision of the Organiser in relation to imposing penalties is final.
